summary: Two Khajitt bros dream of one day roaming the world and fighting dragons
descriptionHtml:
Meet the Khajiit Brothers, who live alone outside Dawnstar.

Do Ziri is much taller then the average Khajiit, slightly older of the two, and is a Swordsman. He wears Steel Armor, is level 15, and cannot die.

Lucky is the smaller, cheakier of the two. He is a Ranger, level 10, cannot die.I cannot make them make them marriagable without changing their voices. 

These guys are GOOD, RELIABLE, and CUTE

If the download manager button does not work please download manually, and let me know

To find them, just head past Dawnstar, past the DB santuary, and you\'ll see a tent. Thats them. Check map.

Im sorry if things may seem wrong as The medicines make my hands unbeariblt shaky and i had trouble placing things on the ground.

As i took the photos, we were attacked by two dragons, you may see the skeletons in the background. I had plans on a third female khajiit, but I had problems. She will come at a later date

Have fun.
Steam   http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=84959828
Check out my other mods on Steam.
